								</td><br>
								이미지 업로드<br><input type="file" name="filename" ><br>
								<button style="float:right;  margin-right: 5px" class="py-3 px-4 bg-primary text-white border-0 rounded font-weight-bold" type="submit">정보 수정</button>
    							<input style="float:right;  margin-right: 5px" class="py-3 px-4 bg-primary text-white border-0 rounded font-weight-bold" type="button" id="btnRtn" name="return" value="돌아가기">
								
